00:42:17.040 --> 00:42:20.790
They were always considered white,
all Syrians were considered white

00:42:20.790 --> 00:42:25.780
until the '20s when people
began to worry about that

00:42:25.780 --> 00:42:29.530
for citizenship purposes
and there were some - well,

00:42:29.530 --> 00:42:35.600
the first citizenship trial with
the Syrians was in 1909 actually,

00:42:35.600 --> 00:42:38.910
